heroes.name: npc_dota_hero_enchantress
heroes.bio_loc:
Aiushtha appears to be an innocent, carefree creature of the woods, and while this is certainly true, it is hardly the sum of her story. She well understands the suffering of the natural world. She has wandered far, and fared through forests bright and drear, in every clime and every season, gathering friends, sharing news, bringing laughter and healing wherever she goes. For in worlds wracked by war, forests are leveled for the building of ships and siege engines; and even in places of peace, the woods are stripped for the building of homes, and as fuel for countless hearths.

Aiushtha hears the pleas of the small creatures, the furtive folk who need green shade and a leafy canopy to thrive. She lends her ears to those who have no other listeners. She carries their stories from the wood to the world, believing that her own good cheer is a kind of Enchantment, that can itself fulfill the promise of a verdant future.
heroes.hype_loc: Harmful up close and lethal at a distance, Enchantress skewers foes with attacks imbued to become more damaging the further they fly. Whether inflicting powerful slows on her enemies or charming forest creatures to fight her battles, she is never short of tools to win a fight.
heroes.npe_desc_loc: Enchants neutral creeps to do her bidding

abilities.name: enchantress_impetus
abilities.desc_loc: Places an enchantment on each attack while activated, causing it to deal additional damage based on how far away the target is.  The farther the target, the greater the damage dealt. Deals double damage to creeps and illusions.
abilities.lore_loc: While Aiushtha favors peaceful means, she is capable of a magical onslaught from a distance, her spears gaining energy from the natural life around her.
notes_loc: The damage is capped at %distance_cap% distance.
Distance to target is measured when the projectile hits.

abilities.name: enchantress_enchant
abilities.desc_loc:
Enchantress charms an enemy. If the enemy is a hero, they are slowed and damaged for %slow_duration%s.

 If the enemy is a creep, she brings it under her control, increasing its attack damage and max health. Enchantress can control up to %max_creeps% creeps at a time for up to %dominate_duration%s. 

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel
abilities.lore_loc: A true steward of the forest, Aiushtha befriends all within it - from lowly trolls to powerful centaurs.
abilities.scepter_loc: Enchantress can control multiple creeps at a time.

abilities.name: enchantress_natures_attendants
abilities.desc_loc: A cloud of wisps heals Enchantress and any friendly units nearby. Lasts %abilityduration% seconds.
abilities.lore_loc: Whimsical spirits of the woods possess a healing power that is quite subtle, but gains strength in numbers.
notes_loc: Units with full HP will not be selected for the heal.
abilities.shard_loc: Adds %shard_permanent_wisp_count% permanent Nature's Attendants that follow Enchantress around.

abilities.name: enchantress_bunny_hop
abilities.desc_loc: Leaps backward, dodges incoming projectiles, and launches an Impetus attack on the %attack_targets% furthest enemy units within Enchantress' attack range + %bonus_attack_range%.

abilities.name: enchantress_little_friends
abilities.desc_loc: Enchantress roots an enemy unit. All creeps, ally, enemy and neutral within a radius will gain bonus movement and attack speed and attack the chosen target for %duration% seconds.

abilities.name: enchantress_untouchable
abilities.desc_loc: Enchantress beguiles her enemies, slowing their attacks when she is attacked.
abilities.lore_loc: After attacking Aiushtha, most opponents are overwhelmed with guilt having attacked such a natural beauty.
notes_loc: All units who directly attack Enchantress will get slowed.
The slow is applied on the attacking unit when the attack starts, not when damage is applied.
